    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Denial. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Anger. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Bargaining. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Depression. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead a lone path of vengeance, as you step closer to your ultimate choice. In which way will you come to <i>acceptance? </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this story of grief, suffering, and faith - shoot your way through the criminal organization responsible for the death of your woman. You must learn how to out-maneuver your foes as the odds stack against you and your goal of toppling their slimy syndicate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Featuring: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20 levels of increasing difficulty</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 different guns to adapt to</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 extraordinary enemy types</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Frantic fighting around every corner</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ample RNG for unpredictability</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A substantial soundtrack</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A secret level...</strong></p></li></ul>",
